1 . sudo apt-get install maven

configuratio from STS 

1. in STS , 
   window > preference > Maven
   select what you need to have 
   apply 

2. restart STS 

create new maven project 

1. file > new > other > Maven > Maven project > next > select a archietype(quickstart template) > group id : like package name (com.tauwab.test) ,artifact id : project name like MavenProject > finish

